name: Autumn Style
description:
This is a DreamArtist Textual Inversion Style Embedding trained on a single image of fall/autumn like colors. You can get amazing autumn/fall color effects in your images by calling Style-Autumn in the positive prompt, and if you want to temper the effect, also call Style-Autumn-neg in the negative prompt.

If you'd like the effect to come through stronger (some models need it), try bumping up the emphasis on Style-Autumn - see the images below.

Please consider joining my Patreon! Advanced SD tutorials, settings explanations, adult-art, from a female content creator (me!) patreon.com/theally

Props to Elldreth for the many hours spent figuring this all out with me! Go check his models.
